https://www.amazon.com/Paradigms-Artificial-Intelligence-Programming-Studies/dp/1558601910/ref=sr_1_1?dchild=1&amp;keywords=paradigms+of+artificial+intelligence&amp;qid=1600610453&amp;s=books&amp;sr=1-1
